<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/"> <soap:Header/> <soap:Body> <ns:BrowseNodeLookup xmlns:ns="http://webservices.amazon.com/AWSECommerceService/2011-08-01"> <ns:MarketplaceDomain>{$BrowseNodeLookup/MarketplaceDomain/text()}</ns:MarketplaceDomain> <ns:AWSAccessKeyId>{$BrowseNodeLookup/AWSAccessKeyId/text()}</ns:AWSAccessKeyId> <ns:AssociateTag>{$BrowseNodeLookup/AssociateTag/text()}</ns:AssociateTag> <ns:Validate>{$BrowseNodeLookup/Validate/text()}</ns:Validate> <ns:XMLEscaping>{$BrowseNodeLookup/XMLEscaping/text()}</ns:XMLEscaping> <ns:Shared> { for $BrowseNodeId in $BrowseNodeLookup/Shared/BrowseNodeId return <ns:BrowseNodeId>{$BrowseNodeId/text()}</ns:BrowseNodeId> }
